dct_title_s: Il vero disego della citadi Tunis e Biserta
dct_description_sm: North oriented toward bottom of sheet.
Pictorial vignettes of settlements (including fortifications), soldiers, ships.
Appears in Camocio's Isole famose, porti, fortezze e terre marittime sottoposte alla Ser. Sig. di Venetia, Venice, 1572.
